These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: video-games, reading, chess, fishing, filmmaking
The people have 5 different jobs:  teacher, architect, engineer, librarian, designer
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, airplane, snowmobile, taxi
There are 5 different favourite colors: ivory, purple, lavender, aquamarine, fuchsia
 1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 2. the engineer is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the designer is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 5. the person who likes ivory is the teacher##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person driving the jet-ski and the designer##2
12. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the architect##1
13. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Hobby      | video-games        | reading | filmmaking     | chess   | fishing |
| Job   | engineer     | architect      | librarian | designer   | teacher    |
| Transport   | snowmobile  | jet-ski     | helicopter | airplane | taxi  |
| Color           | purple | lavender      | fuchsia     | aquamarine   | ivory     |

