.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, aquamarine, ebony, black, lilac
The people have 5 different jobs:  freelancer, manager, bartender, firefighter, videographer
There 5 different types of food: peas, garlic, lime, pineapple, pomegranate
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: satire, time-travel, sports, western, thriller
 1. the person watching thriller movies is in the middle##1
 2. the videographer is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
 3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 4. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person eating peas and the videographer##2
 6. the person watching western movies is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 7. the freelancer is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 8. the person eating lime is the firefighter##1
 9. the person eating lime is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
10. the bartender is on the right of the manager##1
11. the person eating lime is the person who likes ebony##1
12. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Color         | black | grey | lilac    | aquamarine  | ebony    |
| Job   | videographer    | manager       | bartender      | freelancer | firefighter        |
| Food   | pomegranate   | garlic     | peas    | pineapple  | lime     |
| Movie-Genre     | sports    | time-travel | thriller | western | satire |

