.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
There are 5 different nationalities: japanese, spanish, german, turkish, pakistani
There 5 different types of food: garlic, lime, artichoke, grapes, spinach
House: colonial, farmhouse, palace, tower, futuristic
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, sunflower, tulip, dahlia, lily
 1. the pakistani is the farmhouse house##1
 2. the person who growsdahlia is in the middle##1
 3. the tower house is in the middle##1
 4. the person eating garlic is in the middle##1
 5. the pakistani is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 6. the spanish is on the left of the colonial house##1
 7. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 8. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 9. the palace house is on the far left##1
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person eating grapes##1
11. the german is on the right of the person who growslily##1
12. the turkish is on the right of the futuristic house##1
13. the person who growslily is between the person eating spinach and the german##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Nationality         | japanese | pakistani     | german   | spanish   | turkish |
| Food   | spinach  | lime | garlic | grapes | artichoke        |
| House   | palace      | farmhouse      | tower       | futuristic       | colonial       |
| Flower         | sunflower | lily  | dahlia    | balloon-flower    | tulip        |

