.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
5 different pets are kept: turtle, bird, chinchilla, guinea-pig, frog
5 different games are played: backgammon, chess, monopoly, poker, mah-jongg
House: modern, ranch-style, gothic-revival, tower, wooden
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, poppy, rose, daisy, begonia
 1. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 4. the person who growsbegonia is between the tower house and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
 5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the wooden house is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 7. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is the ranch-style house##1
 9. the wooden house is in the middle##1
10. the tower house is the person who growsamaryllis##1
11. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
12. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
13. the ranch-style house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Pet          | frog  | chinchilla     | guinea-pig   | bird     | turtle |
| Game         | mah-jongg | backgammon    | monopoly  | poker | chess   |
| House   | ranch-style        | modern    | wooden     | gothic-revival     | tower    |
| Flower   | poppy    | rose | daisy | begonia | amaryllis   |

