.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: brown, chestnut, purple, blood-red, lilac
House: gothic-revival, wooden, cottage, futuristic, victorian
5 different games are played: poker, whist, bridge, snooker, backgammon
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: epic, adventure, horror, comedy, scientific
 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 2. the futuristic house is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 4. the person who likes purple is between the person watching adventure movies and the gothic-revival house##2
 5. the victorian house is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 6. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 7. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is on the far right##1
10. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person playing poker##1
11. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the cottage house##1
12. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing poker##1
13. the cottage house is on the right of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Color   | blood-red       | lilac       | brown   | purple      | chestnut    |
| House       | victorian | futuristic        | gothic-revival       | cottage       | wooden |
| Game        | backgammon     | whist        | snooker | poker        | bridge  |
| Movie-Genre      | comedy | horror | epic      | scientific | adventure  |

