5 different pets are kept: ferret, dog, goldfish, rabbit, snake
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, april, march, may, october
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is in the middle##1
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 3. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
 4. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 6. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 8. the person traveling to paris is the owner of the ferret##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is between the person traveling to paris and the person who growszinnia##2
12. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
13. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |    5    |
