.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: disaster, thriller, comedy, sports, superhero
House: cape-cod, cottage, victorian, farmhouse, ranch-style
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, social-worker, security-guard, coach, musician
5 different pets are kept: lizard, dog, horse, guinea-pig, ferret
 1. the musician is between the owner of the dog and the social-worker##2
 2. the security-guard is on the left of the coach##1
 3. the person watching thriller movies is the farmhouse house##1
 4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the musician##1
 5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 6. the farmhouse house is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the victorian house is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the cape-cod house is on the left of the victorian house##1
10. the security-guard is on the far left##1
11. the owner of the horse is between the security-guard and the victorian house##2
12. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
13. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Movie-Genre    | comedy       | sports    | superhero | thriller  | disaster        |
| House       | ranch-style | cape-cod | victorian  | farmhouse | cottage    |
| Job       | security-guard        | coach   | social-worker  | musician   | dancer |
| Pet   | guinea-pig       | horse      | ferret      | lizard | dog  |

