5 different pets are kept: frog, turtle, goat, lizard, hedgehog
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: poppy, amaryllis, lily, aconite, tulip
 1. the person who growslily is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the owner of the goat and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 3. the person traveling to hannover is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 5. the owner of the frog is in the middle##1
 6. the person traveling to hannover is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who growsamaryllis##2
 7. the person who growsaconite is the person traveling to miami##1
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who growslily##1
 9. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
11. the person who's hobby is writing is the owner of the turtle##1
12. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
13. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
