.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, march, october, june, april
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, zinnia, orchid, begonia, marigold
There are 5 different favourite colors: green, apricot, black, coral, ivory
There 5 different types of food: nectarine, blueberry, potato, spinach, pepper
 1. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 4. the person eating potato is on the far left##1
 5. the person who likes apricot is between the person who growssunflower and the person who likes green##2
 6. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person eating nectarine and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in august##2
 9. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
10. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Birthday         | april  | october | june   | march      | august |
| Flower   | sunflower   | begonia    | zinnia | marigold | orchid      |
| Color           | black | apricot    | green       | coral     | ivory      |
| Food     | potato | pepper        | nectarine  | blueberry        | spinach    |

