.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
5 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, backgammon, monopoly, snooker
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, tea, cola, almond-milk
The people have 5 different jobs:  lawyer, electrician, entrepreneur, analyst, bartender
The people use 5 different means of transport: van, snowmobile, helicopter, taxi, train
 1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person driving the taxi and the bartender##2
 3. the bartender is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is the lawyer##1
 5. the lawyer is between the person driving the train and the entrepreneur##2
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 7. the person drinking tea is the analyst##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is the electrician##1
 9. the person driving the van is the electrician##1
10. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
12. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Game         | backgammon    | snooker  | mah-jongg  | whist      | monopoly |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | almond-milk   | cola | tea | 7up   |
| Job   | entrepreneur | lawyer    | bartender    | analyst       | electrician         |
| Transport   | taxi  | snowmobile | train    | helicopter     | van      |

 